{"tid":1216362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢夢到] 愛國不愛黨 林鄭救香港!!!","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:25:17.000Z","uid":135551,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7170b87d571d380440a0078fc417496c0a0afdb3","tid":1216362,"uid":135551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"中央熊仔都係咁話修例唔關佢地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推曬個波比林鄭想同佢割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係林鄭呢個時候都係唔退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至背負全港罵名都要硬推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇諗過點解???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係人都知，香港就算一國兩制係共產黨之下都會被一步步蠶食同赤化，要真正解放香港就只有解決製造問題源頭嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭之所以咁無理強推就係要引起國際關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢背負千古罪名都要引八國聯軍入關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的就係將共慘黨連根拔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢救嘅唔單止係香港🇭🇰<br />\n更加係全個中國大陸!!!!解放13億同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭先係真正拯救香港嘅民族英雄!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d092ea1af119e618aaf79b1c9e7f0d00e2ef5d","tid":1216362,"uid":196924,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"佢已經成功救咗台灣<img src=